{"tid":2198644,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[求答]牆身太窄不適合做趟門櫃？","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T03:06:22.000Z","uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"554023336a075cceeddd76f8f646e36a44fc9574","tid":2198644,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kyxkn91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKyxkn91.jpg&h=3336f977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，以上係我家睡房既圖則，最近想訂造一個到頂既趟門衣櫃，但有傢俬舖同我講個牆身唔夠5呎唔適合做趟門櫃，驚容易壞同難趟。請問當中原因係咩？牆身太窄就唔適合做趟門櫃？求大神解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f789bc214e7dfb795e1de93e5b3f17b896d3f6","tid":2198644,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"牆身5呎<br />\n個趟門就得2呎闊<br />\n但係6呎高<br />\n又窄又長就真係..."},{"pid":"4ae77831ab62eb74339e7cd3f01a4aa2d5672f00","tid":2198644,"uid":316667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4f789bc214e7dfb795e1de93e5b3f17b896d3f6","tid":2198644,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"牆身5呎<br />\n個趟門就得2呎闊<br />\n但係6呎高<br />\n又窄又長就真係..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"多謝你解答，我諗住做兩層，下面雙趟門，上面頂櫃平開門"},{"pid":"27e12e262589e301438498365767a718f3fbbf84","tid":2198644,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"個門相對易彎 有問題機率係較大"},{"pid":"0a3839d0acaed37830e372b57138b806078d67ae","tid":2198644,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"你想用趟門<br />\n斷鳩估應該係覺得推拉門打開佔空間覺得唔方便<br />\n<br />\n但趟門一邊門得兩呎幾係窄左少少，攞野放野都唔多舒服<br />\n<br />\n比我揀會整摺門"},{"pid":"4781a1cc890ce7ec11195d0898997cdc0b213170","tid":2198644,"uid":170512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:09:0